Title: An NBA Top Shot highlight of an epic LeBron James dunk just sold for $200K
Description: We’ve seen a few highlights sell for $100,000, and now there’s a record-breaker that sold for $208,000 (!!!). It’s a moment in which LeBron James dunked all over Nemanja Bjelica as the Sacramento Kings forward attempted to take a charge back in 2019.
Author: USA Today on MSN.com
